# Project Instructions

## Cognitive Tools

These cortex tools are always available via the `mcp__cortex__*` namespace.

| When this happens | Call this |
|---|---|
| Starting any session | `query("what was I working on")` |
| Exploring any topic | `query("the topic")` — pull related memories first |
| Something interesting happened | `observe("what you noticed")` — capture it now |
| A belief shifts | `believe("the new position")` |
| Validating a conclusion | `validate("the claim")` |
| Mapping knowledge about X | `neighbors("concept name")` |

**The rule:** if you're about to write something, you should have already called `query()` or `observe()` in the same session.
